forkee.name: eShopOnContainers
forkee.description: Cross-platform .NET sample microservices and container based application that runs on Linux Windows and macOS. Powered by .NET 7, Docker Containers and Azure Kubernetes Services. Supports Visual Studio, VS for Mac and CLI based environments with Docker CLI, dotnet CLI, VS Code or any other code editor.

issue.title: Any reason I cannot to connect to service and container?
issue.body:
When I use docker compose up, I can connect service like web status with localhost:5107. But when I start it in Visual Studio 2022. I cannot connect to any although the containers all up and good. Any idea?

Also, with docker compose up, I cannot connect to the sql instance in the container with localhost:5433 from SSMS, what could be the problem?

Thanks
